  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835180/extras/d25243ba62dbdfee31c70e1b263cb3db.apng?t=1768952998\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835180/extras/d25243ba62dbdfee31c70e1b263cb3db.poster.avif?t=1768952998\" class=\"bb_img\" width=654 height=120 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835180/extras/38a0fa3fc347316711e2426e4d482229.webp?t=1768952998\" width=520 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Play the prequel of Linked Mask!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Incarnate yourself in the skin of Viewer, a curious traveler who has been called by the gods to fulfill an objective that is not very clear, but you're here. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A 2D platformer with a gradual difficulty but at no time taking you by the hand to overcome the different challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835180/extras/7ec35f87b02220c799f0689d9dd8ac88.poster.avif?t=1768952998\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835180/extras/7ec35f87b02220c799f0689d9dd8ac88.webm?t=1768952998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835180/extras/7ec35f87b02220c799f0689d9dd8ac88.mp4?t=1768952998\" ty